  {"id":"lgP_14012","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"How do you prioritize competing tasks?","ja":"競合するタスクをどう優先しますか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14013","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Describe a mistake and what you learned.","ja":"失敗とそこから学んだことを教えてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14014","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"What kind of work environment suits you?","ja":"どんな職場環境が合っていますか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14015","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"How can I help you today?","ja":"本日はどうされましたか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14016","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"Is there anything else?","ja":"他に何かありますか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14019","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"Your order is on its way.","ja":"ご注文は配送中です。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14021","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"I'll escalate this to a specialist.","ja":"担当者に引き継ぎます。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14022","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"We'll process your refund shortly.","ja":"まもなく返金処理いたします。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14024","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Is this resolving your issue?","ja":"これで解決しそうですか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14025","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"I understand how frustrating this must be.","ja":"さぞお困りのことと存じます。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14026","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let me make sure I have this right.","ja":"認識に相違がないか確認させてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14027","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"We've credited your account accordingly.","ja":"それに応じてご返金いたしました。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14028","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"I'll personally follow up to confirm.","ja":"私が責任を持って確認いたします。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14029","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Rest assured, we'll make this right.","ja":"必ず正しく対応いたしますのでご安心ください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14030","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Let's review the main points.","ja":"要点を復習しましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14031","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Can you summarize the chapter?","ja":"その章を要約できますか。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14032","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"This concept builds on the last one.","ja":"この概念は前回の続きです。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14033","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Take notes on the key terms.","ja":"重要語をメモしてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14034","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"We'll cover this in the next lecture.","ja":"これは次回の講義で扱います。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14035","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's examine the evidence critically.","ja":"証拠を批判的に検討しましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14036","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The data supports the hypothesis.","ja":"データは仮説を支持しています。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14037","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Consider the broader implications.","ja":"より広い意味合いを考えてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14038","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"This theory has notable limitations.","ja":"この理論には顕著な限界があります。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14039","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Compare and contrast the two approaches.","ja":"二つの手法を比較対照してください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14040","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The findings warrant further study.","ja":"その結果はさらなる研究を要します。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14041","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Cite your sources properly.","ja":"出典を正しく引用してください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14042","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The argument hinges on this assumption.","ja":"議論はこの前提にかかっています。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14043","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Correlation does not imply causation.","ja":"相関は因果を意味しません。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14044","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's situate this in its context.","ja":"これを文脈の中に位置づけましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14046","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"Help yourself to some food.","ja":"ご自由に食べてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14047","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"Thanks for having me.","ja":"お招きありがとう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14048","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"This is for you.","ja":"これ、どうぞ。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14049","type":"dictation","level":"A2","text":"Let me introduce my friend.","ja":"友達を紹介します。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14050","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"It was lovely meeting you.","ja":"お会いできて嬉しかったです。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14051","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"We should do this again sometime.","ja":"また今度やりましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14052","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"I've heard so much about you.","ja":"お噂はかねがね。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14053","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Let me get you a drink.","ja":"飲み物を持ってきます。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14054","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Don't be a stranger.","ja":"また連絡してね。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14055","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"I really appreciate you coming.","ja":"来てくれて本当に感謝します。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14056","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"I hope I'm not intruding.","ja":"お邪魔でなければいいのですが。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14057","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Feel free to stay as long as you like.","ja":"好きなだけいてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14058","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"It's been far too long.","ja":"本当に久しぶりですね。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14059","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's keep this tradition going.","ja":"この恒例を続けましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14060","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Something's not working.","ja":"何かがうまく動きません。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14061","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Let's troubleshoot this step by step.","ja":"順を追って原因を調べましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14063","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"That should fix the problem.","ja":"それで問題は直るはずです。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14064","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Let me know if it happens again.","ja":"また起きたら教えてください。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14065","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's isolate what's causing this.","ja":"原因を切り分けましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14066","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"We need a workaround for now.","ja":"当面は代替策が必要です。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14067","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"This is a recurring issue.","ja":"これは繰り返し起きる問題です。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14068","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's get to the root of it.","ja":"根本原因を突き止めましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14069","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"I'll document the steps to reproduce it.","ja":"再現手順を記録します。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14070","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"We've ruled out the obvious causes.","ja":"明らかな原因は除外しました。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14071","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's not patch over the symptom.","ja":"症状だけを取り繕わないようにしましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14072","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The fix introduced a new problem.","ja":"修正が新たな問題を生みました。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14073","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"We need to address this at the source.","ja":"根本から対処する必要があります。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14074","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Let's verify the fix in staging first.","ja":"まず検証環境で修正を確認しましょう。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14075","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"It all started one quiet morning.","ja":"それはある静かな朝に始まった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14076","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Little did they know what was coming.","ja":"彼らはこれから起きることを知らなかった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14077","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Years passed before the truth came out.","ja":"真実が明らかになるまで何年もかかった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14078","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"Against all odds, she succeeded.","ja":"あらゆる困難に逆らい、彼女は成功した。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14079","type":"dictation","level":"B1","text":"The journey changed him forever.","ja":"その旅は彼を永遠に変えた。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14080","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"What seemed like a setback became a turning point.","ja":"挫折に見えたことが転機になった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14081","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Looking back, the signs were there all along.","ja":"振り返れば、兆候は最初からあった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14082","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The decision would haunt him for years.","ja":"その決断は何年も彼を悩ませることになる。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14083","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"In hindsight, it was the right call.","ja":"今思えば、それは正しい判断だった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14084","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The town was never quite the same again.","ja":"その町は二度と元には戻らなかった。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14085","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"Fate, it seemed, had other plans.","ja":"運命には別の計画があったようだ。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14086","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"One small choice rippled through everything.","ja":"一つの小さな選択が全てに波及した。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14087","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"The legacy lived on long after.","ja":"その遺産はその後も長く生き続けた。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14088","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"They say history repeats itself.","ja":"歴史は繰り返すと言われる。"},
  {"id":"lgP_14089","type":"dictation","level":"B2","text":"And so, a new chapter began.","ja":"こうして、新たな章が始まった。"}
